<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
   <div rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="Aink219-kilavi"> varaiviṭai vaittup pirinta vaṇumaikkaṇṇē āṟṟāḷākiya talaimakaṭkut tōḻi kūṟiyatu.  </p>
      <p xml:lang="en"> What the confidante told the heroine, who could not bear, in the recency of [the hero] placing a gap in the marriage and separating.  </p>
   </div>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink219">
<l>karuṅkāl vēṅkai māttakaṭ ṭoḷvī</l>
<l>yiruṅkal viyalaṟai varippat tāa</l>
<l>naṉmalai nāṭaṉ pirinteṉa</l>
<l>voṇṇutal pacappa tevaṉko laṉṉāy</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Mother, why does your bright forehead grow pale, </l>
<l>[just] because the man from the land of the good mountains, </l>
<l rend="space indent">where bright flowers with large outer petals of the black-trunked Kino tree</l>
<l rend="indent">spread expansively on the big stones and wide rocks, </l>
<l rend="space">had separated? </l>

      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
